  "title": "Automation Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We are hiring an Automation Engineer who\nspecializes in Ansible to automate provisioning, configuration management, and\ninfrastructure orchestration across hybrid environments.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>·       \nDevelop and maintain Ansible\nplaybooks, roles, and automation pipelines</p><p>·       \nAutomate OS patching,\nconfiguration, compliance, and hardening</p><p>·       \nIntegrate Ansible into CI/CD\nworkflows and infrastructure pipelines</p><p>·       \nMaintain inventory, secrets,\nand automation governance standards</p><p>·       \nTroubleshoot automation\nfailures and drive continuous improvement</p><p>·       \nSupport IaC and infrastructure\nautomation initiatives</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>·       \n3+ years of automation or\nconfiguration management experience</p><p>·       \nStrong hands-on Ansible\nexpertise (playbooks, roles, modules)</p><p>·       \nProficiency with Linux/Windows\nsystem administration</p><p>·       \nScripting skills in Python or\nShell</p><p>·       \nUnderstanding of cloud\nplatforms (Azure/AWS)</p>",
